(b) (6)                 While these numbers may not seem to reflect a great unmet need, our PRC budget is substantially supplemented by tribal 3rd party funds to meet the referral needs of our service area. Our 2021 funding from IHS was approximately $1.8 million. We spent an additional $2 million dollars on referred care last year. Financial need is certainly justified when federal dollars cover less than half of our referred care costs.
